Miss Rong, if you didn't know me,

00:02:20.430 --> 00:02:21.240
why did you

00:02:21.240 --> 00:02:22.630
judge me with such malice?

00:02:22.630 --> 00:02:23.120
You...

00:02:24.090 --> 00:02:25.120
